Class UpgradeUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.upgrade.UpgradeUtils

  • public class UpgradeUtils
extends Object
    This class contains utilities to upgrade the service schema configuration to be compatible with OpenAM.

      • createService

        public static void createService(String xml,
                                 NewServiceWrapper newServiceModifications,
                                 SSOToken adminToken)
                          throws UpgradeException
        This will parse the given XML and create the service specified within. Once the service has been created the given NewServiceWrapper will be used to apply any modifications specified for the new service.
        Parameters:
        xml - The XML text describing the new service.
        newServiceModifications - The NewServiceWrapper that contains the modification to the new service.
        adminToken - The sso token.
        Throws:
        UpgradeException - If an upgrade error occurs.
